## Common Issues & Solutions

### Visibility Issues
- Sections should be visible by default (opacity: 1)
- Animation adds `animate-in` class on scroll, but doesn't control initial visibility
- Check CSS for any `opacity: 0` without proper animation triggers

### Image Sizing
- Testimonials image: max-width 700px, centered
- Instructor image: No hover scale (prevents whitespace issue)
- Section images: Full-width in their columns

### Footer Spacing
- Two main columns: left (brand) and right (grouped columns)
- Spacing controlled with `gap` on `.footerColumnsGroup` (not between main columns)

### Animation Performance
- Use CSS transforms, not layout properties
- Sections animate on viewport entry
- Hero elements animate on first load with staggered delays

